longBusinessSummary: KOALA Financial Group Limited, an investment holding company, engages in securities brokerage, share placements, underwriting, and money lending activities in Hong Kong. It is involved in the provision of brokerage, margin and short-term IPO financing, and placing and underwriting services, as well as personal and corporate loans; securities and properties investment, and asset management activities; and leasing investment properties. The company was formerly known as Sunrise (China) Technology Group Limited and changed its name to KOALA Financial Group Limited in June 2017. KOALA Financial Group Limited is headquartered in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
